The '''Thesme Trace''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] located in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]. The Thesme Trace intersected with the [[Hydian Way/Legends|Hydian Way]] and the [[Gordian Reach/Legends|Gordian Reach]] at the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Feriae Junction/Legends|Feriae Junction]] in the [[Thesme sector/Legends|Thesme sector]].

